name: The Beauty of Weeds
description:
Title: The Beauty of Weeds
Location: Forest Grove, Oregon
Year Taken: 2018
About this photo: My in-laws have a 5 acre property with a wood shop, greenhouses, and no lack of backdrops for great photographs. I spent time with Erica, a local optometry student having fun with modeling here and there, and we created some cool images. She wanted to incorporate the little dandelions into a couple shots. My goal with this piece was to take the focus on the dandelion theme was to make the entire piece of artwork look and feel like a pretty little weed.
